  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_830326\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1952239_830326\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481855\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1952239_481855\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Biological Soil Crusts</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1952242\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-right\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/nature/images/CryptobioticNH.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"Cryptogamic crusts, N. Herbert NPS\" src=\"/grca/learn/nature/images/CryptobioticNH.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Cryptogamic crusts <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS Photo by N. Herbert</p></figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\nBiological crusts (also known as cryptogamic, microbiotic, crytobiotic and microphytic crusts) are microscopic non-vascular assemblages composed of blue-green algae, diatoms, golden brown algae, lichens, mosses and a few xerophytic (adapted for growth with a limited water supply) liverworts on more mesic (moderate amount of moisture) sites. <br/>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_1952241\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_1952241\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-left\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/nature/images/crustlogo.gif\" type=\"image/gif\"/>\n<img alt=\"Don't bust the cryptogamic crust logo\" src=\"/grca/learn/nature/images/crustlogo.gif\" title=\"\"/>\n</picture>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\nBlue-green algae contribute to the bulk of the algal tissue. Biological crusts grow on and within soils and other substrates, modifying these surfaces in significant ways. The blue-green algae fix atmospheric nitrogen and thus enhance the nutrient status of the soil.<br/>\n<br/>\nCryptogamic crusts retard erosion by wind and water, help retain soil moisture during dry periods, slow evaporation rates, and enhance seedling establishment. These living crusts are extremely fragile and one footprint can set back development for decades.<br/>\n<br/>\nFor more information on Biological Soil Crusts visit this <a href=\"http://www.soilcrust.org/\" id=\"http://www.soilcrust.org/|\">USGS Soilcrust website</a>.\n</div></div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: February 24, 2015</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
